#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:1 of
msgid "Exponentially scaled modified Bessel function of the second kind."
msgstr "指数缩放的第二类变形贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns the exponentially scaled, modified Bessel function of the second "
"kind (sometimes called the third kind) for real order `v` at complex "
"`z`::"
msgstr ""
"返回在复数 `z` 处实数阶 `v` 的指数缩放的第二类变形贝塞尔函数（有时称为"
"第三类）::"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kve.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:9 of
msgid "Order of Bessel functions"
msgstr "贝塞尔函数的阶"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:11 of
msgid "Argument at which to evaluate the Bessel functions"
msgstr "用于计算贝塞尔函数的自变量"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:13 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "可选的函数结果输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kve.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:16 of
msgid "The exponentially scaled modified Bessel function of the second kind."
msgstr "指数缩放的第二类变形贝塞尔函数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kve.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`kv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:22 of
msgid "This function without exponential scaling."
msgstr "不带指数缩放的此函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`k0e`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:25 of
msgid "Faster version of this function for order 0."
msgstr "阶数为 0 时此函数的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`k1e`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:28 of
msgid "Faster version of this function for order 1."
msgstr "阶数为 1 时此函数的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kve:32 of
msgid ""
"Wrapper for AMOS [1]_ routine `zbesk`.  For a discussion of the algorithm"
" used, see [2]_ and the references therein."
msgstr ""
"AMOS [1]_ 例程 `zbesk` 的封装。有关所用算法的讨论，请参见 [2]_ 及其中的"
"参考文献。"

